\c 38
\s Ukukhutshwa kukaJeremiya emgodini
\p
\v 1 UShefathiya indodana kaMathani, loGedaliya indodana kaPashuri, loJukali indodana kaShelemiya,\x + 37.3\x* loPashuri indodana kaMalikiya,\x + 21.1. 1 Lan. 9.12.\x* sebezwile amazwi uJeremiya ayewakhuluma kubo bonke abantu esithi:\x + 21.8.\x*
\v 2 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Osala kulumuzi uzakufa ngenkemba, ngendlala, langomatshayabhuqe wesifo;\x + 21.9; 37.17,18.\x* kodwa ophuma aye kumaKhaladiya uzaphila,\x + 21.9; 37.17,18.\x* ngoba uzakuba lempilo yakhe ibe yimpango, aphile.
\v 3 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Lumuzi uzanikelwa isibili esandleni sebutho lenkosi yeBhabhiloni,\x + 21.10; 32.3.\x* elizawuthumba.\x + 34.22.\x*
\v 4 Iziphathamandla zasezisithi enkosini: Ake abulawe lumuntu,\x + 26.11.\x* ngoba ngalindlela uyekethisa izandla zamadoda empi asele kulumuzi,\x + 6.24.\x* lezandla zabo bonke abantu, ngokukhuluma kibo amazwi anje; ngoba lumuntu kadingi ukuthula kwalababantu, kodwa okubi.
\v 5 Inkosi uZedekhiya yasisithi: Khangela, usesandleni senu, ngoba inkosi kayilakho okuphambene lani ngalutho.\x + 37.17,24,25,26,27.\x*
\v 6 Basebemthatha uJeremiya, bamphosela emgodini kaMalikiya indodana yenkosi,\x + 37.16.\x* owawusegumeni lentolongo,\x + 32.2; 37.13,28.\x* bamehlisa uJeremiya ngamagoda; kwakungelamanzi emgodini,\x + Gen. 37.24. Zek. 9.11.\x* kodwa udaka; uJeremiya wasetshona odakeni.\x + Hlab. 69.14.\x*
\p
\v 7 Kwathi uEbedimeleki\x + 37.8,10,11,12; 39.16.\x* umEthiyophiya\x + Seb. 8.27.\x* indoda umthenwa,\x + 29.2. Isai. 56. 3,4,5.\x* owayesendlini yenkosi, esizwa ukuthi uJeremiya bamfake emgodini (lapho inkosi yayihlezi esangweni lakoBhenjamini),\x + 37.13.\x*
\v 8 uEbedimeleki\x + 37.8,10,11,12; 39.16.\x* waphuma endlini yenkosi, wakhuluma lenkosi esithi:
\v 9 Nkosi yami, nkosi, abantu laba benzile okubi ngakho konke abakwenze kuJeremiya umprofethi, abamphosele emgodini, ngoba uzakufa endaweni yakhe\x + Eks. 16.29.\x* ngenxa yendlala, ngoba kakusekho isinkwa emzini.\x + 37.21. Lilo 1.11.\x*
\v 10 Inkosi yasimlaya uEbedimeleki umEthiyophiya,\x + 38.8,10,11,12; 39.16.\x* isithi: Thatha lapha amadoda angamatshumi amathathu ngaphansi kwesandla sakho, umenyule uJeremiya umprofethi emgodini engakafi.
\v 11 Ngakho uEbedimeleki wathatha amadoda ngaphansi kwesandla sakhe,\x + 37.8,10,11,12; 39.16.\x* wangena endlini yenkosi waze waba ngaphansi kwesiphala, wathatha khona izidwedwe ezidabukileyo lezidwedwe ezigugileyo,\x + Josh. 9.5.\x* wazehlisela kuJeremiya emgodini ngamagoda.
\v 12 UEbedimeleki umEthiyophiya\x + 37.8,10,11,12; 39.16.\x* wasesithi kuJeremiya: Ake ufake izidwedwe ezidabukileyo lezigugileyo ngaphansi kwamakhwapha akho ngaphansi kwamagoda.\x + Hez. 13.18.\x* UJeremiya wasesenza njalo.
\v 13 Basebemdonsa uJeremiya ngamagoda,\x + 37 .6.\x* bamenyula emgodini. UJeremiya wasehlala egumeni lentolongo.
\s UZedekhiya uyelulekwa nguJeremiya
\p
\v 14 Inkosi uZedekhiya yasithuma yathatha uJeremiya umprofethi yamusa kuye, ekungeneni kwesithathu okusendlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*. Inkosi yasisithi kuJeremiya: Ngizakubuza udaba, ungangifihleli lutho.
\v 15 UJeremiya wasesithi kuZedekhiya: Uba ngikutshela, kawuyikungibulala lokungibulala yini? Loba ngikweluleka, kawuyikungilalela.
\v 16 Inkosi uZedekhiya yasifunga kuJeremiya ekusithekeni\x + 37.17.\x* isithi: Kuphila kukaJehova\x + Ruthe 3.13.\x* owasenzela lumphefumulo:\x + Isa. 57.16.\x* Isibili kangiyikukubulala, futhi isibili kangiyikukunikela esandleni salamadoda adinga umphefumulo wakho.\x + 37.1,4.\x*
\v 17 UJeremiya wasesithi kuZedekhiya: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wamabandla, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Uba uphuma isibili\x + 27.12; 37 .2,21. 2 Kho. 24.12.\x* uye kuziphathamandla zenkosi yeBhabhiloni,\x + 37.18,22; 39.3.\x* umphefumulo wakho uzaphila,\x + 34.4,5.\x* lalumuzi kawuyikutshiswa ngomlilo; uzaphila wena lendlu yakho.
\v 18 Kodwa uba ungaphumi\x + 27.12; 37 .2,21. 2 Kho. 24.12.\x* uye kuziphathamandla zenkosi yeBhabhiloni,\x + 37.18,22; 39.3.\x* lumuzi uzanikelwa esandleni samaKhaladiya,\x + 21.10; 37.23.\x* awutshise ngomlilo;\x + 21.10; 37.23.\x* lawe kawuyikuphunyuka esandleni sawo.\x + 32.4; 37.23.\x*
\v 19 Inkosi uZedekhiya yasisithi kuJeremiya: Ngiyawesaba amaJuda ahlubukele kumaKhaladiya,\x + 37.13.\x* hlezi anginikele esandleni sawo, angiklolodele.\x + 1 Sam. 31.4.\x*
\v 20 UJeremiya wasesithi: Kawayiku\add ku\add*nikela; ake ulalele ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* njengalelo engilikhuluma kuwe,\x + 34.4,5.\x* khona kukulungele,\x + 40.9.\x* futhi umphefumulo wakho uzaphila.
\v 21 Kodwa uba usala ukuphuma,\x + 27.12. 37 .2,21. 2 Kho. 24.12.\x* yileli ilizwi iN\nd kosi\nd* engibonise lona \add lokuthi\add*:
\v 22 Khangela-ke, bonke abesifazana abasele endlini yenkosi yakoJuda bazakhitshelwa kuziphathamandla zenkosi yeBhabhiloni, bathi: Abangane bakho bakukhuthazile,\x + 43.3. 1 Kho. 21.25.\x* bakwehlula;\x + Obad. 1.7.\x* inyawo zakho zitshone odakeni;\x + Jobe 38.6.\x* babuyele emuva.\x + Isa. 42.17. Hlab. 35.4.\x*
\v 23 Njalo azakhuphela abafazi bonke bakho lamadodana akho kumaKhaladiya;\x + 39.6; 41.10; 43.6; 44.7.\x* lawe kawuyikuphunyuka esandleni sawo,\x + 32.4; 37.23.\x* kodwa uzabanjwa ngesandla senkosi yeBhabhiloni, lalumuzi uzawutshisa ngomlilo.\x + 21.10; 37.23.\x*
\p
\v 24 UZedekhiya wasesithi kuJeremiya: Kakungabi khona umuntu owaziyo lamazwi, khona ungayikufa.
\v 25 Kodwa nxa iziphathamandla zisizwa ukuthi ngikhulume lawe,\x + 37 .5.\x* zize kuwe zithi kuwe: Ake usitshele, ubusithini enkosini, ungakufihli kithi, khona kasiyikukubulala; njalo inkosi ikhulumeni kuwe;
\v 26 uzakuthi-ke kuzo: Mina ngiwise ukuncenga kwami phambi kwenkosi\x + 36.7.\x* ukuthi ingangibuyiseli endlini kaJonathani ukuze ngifele khona.\x + 37.20.\x*
\v 27 Zasezifika zonke iziphathamandla kuJeremiya, zambuza; yena waziphendula njengawo wonke lamazwi inkosi ewalayileyo. Zasezithula kuye, ngoba udaba lwalungezwakali.
\v 28 UJeremiya wasehlala\x + 37.21.\x* egumeni lentolongo kwaze kwaba lusuku iJerusalema eyathunjwa ngalo;\x + 32.2.\x* wayekhona lapho iJerusalema ithunjwa.